feed.title: All Things Iconic
feed.subtitle: All Things Iconic is your one stop destination for today's hot topics. Each week, Jenna Naphtali takes you through the world of pop culture and well, whatever else is on her mind. Stay tuned for special guests, fun games, and a whole lot of laughs. Be sure to listen every Tuesday, it's going to be iconic.

entry.title: Weird Celebrity Couples - Season 1 Episode 1
entry.content:
In Hollywood, you have the “it” couples, the divorcees, and the playboys, but what about those random celebrity couples? Maybe you forgot they dated, or maybe you never knew. This week, Jenna brings on her friend Tatum to delve into the weirdest, most random celebrity couples from the past. They then create some of their own random celebrity pairings, because why not??

Don’t forget to follow on Instagram!
https://www.instagram.com/allthingsiconicpod/
